run build: node scripts/build-inline-resume.js
run local: python3 -m http.server

edit resume data in:
- data/resume.en.json
- data/resume.vn.json

the en resume is inlined into index.html by the build script for faster first render.

github pages:
- workflow file: .github/workflows/deploy-pages.yml
- set Pages source to "GitHub Actions" in repository settings
- push `develop` to run build checks and get a preview artifact from Actions
- deploy production from `main` only
